    "created_at": "2016-02-08T18:34:52Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-05T17:29:38Z",
    "body": "Keep in mind that that Chromium no longer supports XP. The Electron team would have to continue patching Chromium to support XP as well as re-add previous XP specific code the Chromium team striped. And Node.js re-added support but they are likely unsupporting it in v6.\n\nAnd everyone that supports a nonsupported OS are contributing to the problem.\n\nIf you really must, the 0.12.X releases of NW.js use an older version of Chromium thus supporting XP. But NW.js is going to run into the same issue as Electron with their future releases.\n"
  },
